headline: Jack Henry CEO, CFO Featured at Several Upcoming Conferences
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc.® (Nasdaq: JKHY) is pleased to announce that President & CEO Greg Adelson and Chief Financial Officer & Treasurer Mimi Carsley will present at several conferences in the coming weeks.
